tion"><s>Gram-variable, motile, rod-shaped bacteria.</s><s>Round, non-ornamented spores are formed in unswollen sporangia.</s><s>Catalase- and oxidase-negative.</s><s>Main menaquinone is MK-7.</s><s>Predominant lipids are diphosphatidylglycerol, phosphatidylglycerol and an unknown aminophospholipid.</s><s>In addition, two unknown glycolipids and an unknown phosphoglycolipid are present.</s><s>The major fatty acids are anteiso-C<sub>15 : 0</sub> and C<sub>16 : 0</sub>.</s><s>The type species is <em>Saccharibacillus sacchari</em>.</s></p></content></protolog>